snippet.description:

It's also the first time Saaj Bhatt has appeared in a music video. This is the first song from Saaj Bhatt's first album, 'Jannatein'. Stay tuned for the upcoming beautiful melodies from this album!

snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 11 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream- Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 11 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream - 1st February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.title: INDIAN BUDGET EXPLAINED IN 10 MINUTES | Budget 2023 explained | Abhi and Niyu
snippet.description:
In this video, Abhi and Niyu explain the process in which the Union Budget is made and take a look at some of the top spends in the 2023 Union Budget

The Budget is an important document because it signifies the direction that the Government wants to take. It gives a chance to the people to see which ministry takes up most of the resources and understand how much money the Government makes and where they spend it. It is time all of us analyze the data and ask the Government the right questions. 

This video will help you demystify the Budget process and understand the basics of this event

A video by Abhiraj Rajadhyaksha & Niyati Mavinkurve

#budget2023 #finance #economy 

Stay ahead of the game with our exclusive coverage of the Indian Budget 2023. Our in-depth analysis breaks down the latest fiscal policies, economic indicators and their impact on citizens and businesses. Get a complete rundown of government spending and revenue, including allocation for key sectors such as education, health, infrastructure, and more. With expert insights and easy to understand explanations, our video is the go-to source for staying informed on the Indian Budget 2023. Watch now to stay ahead of the curve and make informed decisions.

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3682 - Boss Ne Liya Guruji Ka Aashirvad?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada

Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi

snippet.title: This Valentine's Season In Clash of Clans 💕
snippet.description:
This Valentine's Season, Beast King meets his match... Watch out for Heart Hunter Queen! 


Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. http://supr.cl/ThisArmy

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

https://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service:
https://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/

snippet.title: Women Task Force | Undercover Officer Purvi Gets Hit By The Dangerous Biker Gang | CID | 31 Jan 2023
snippet.description:
There is big planning going on in a stunt bikers' group regarding an event named Mission ABG: JO that is supposed to be held soon. They are planning to commit a bank robbery. The CID team starts catching the members of the group one by one and decodes the secret behind the Mission ABG: JO. Watch the full episode to find out how the CID team cuts through the chase.

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode: 1206
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #livcrime #सीआईडी #NewCID #LatestCID #CID2023

Click here to Subscribe to LIV Crime: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzXpAx4v6rFLYXkJZ5nmSvQ?sub_confirmation=1

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Click here to watch more clips:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0y08jtgaKIW-oBRmsADGpsfuNkU81C

snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 12 Teaser - 1st February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 12 Teaser - 1st February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

snippet.title: தைப்பூசம் 2023 -  தீய சக்தி, நவக்கிரக தோஷங்கள், பகை நீங்க முருகனை வழிபடும் முறை | Thaipusam 2023
snippet.description:
தைப்பூச தினத்தில் முருகனை வழிபடும் முறை, செய்ய வேண்டிய நெய்வேத்தியம், நேரம், படிக்க வேண்டிய பதிகங்கள் என அனைத்து தகவல்களையும் இந்தப் பதிவில் திருமதி. தேச மங்கையர்க்கரசி அம்மா அவர்கள் அளித்துள்ளார். 

வீட்டில் வேல் வழிபாடு செய்யும் முறை | "VEL" Worship method at Home explained by Desa Mangayarkarasi
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eLhE25OaEj8

நாளென் செயும்வினை தானென் செயுமெனை நாடிவந்த
கோளென் செயுங்கொடுங் கூற்றென் செயுங்கும ரேசரிரு
தாளுஞ் சிலம்புஞ் சதங்கையும் தண்டையுஞ் சண்முகமுந்
தோளுங் கடம்பு மெனக்குமுன் னேவந்து தோன்றிடினே

பாடல் 1:
அப்பா நான் வேண்டுதல் கேட்டருள் புரிதல் வேண்டும்
ஆருயிர்கட்கெல்லாம் நான் அன்பு செயல் வேண்டும்
எப்பாரும் எப்பதமும் எங்கணும் நான் சென்றே
எந்தை நினதருட் புகழை இயம்பிடல் வேண்டும்
செப்பாத மேல்நிலைமேல் சுத்த சிவ மார்க்கம்
திகழ்ந்தோங்க அருட்சோதி செலுத்தியிடல் வேண்டும்
தப்பேது நான்செயினும் நீ பொறுத்தல் வேண்டும்
தலைவா நினைப் பிரியாத நிலைமையும் வேண்டுவனே.

பாடல் 2:
ஒருமையுடன் நினது திரு மலரடி நினைக்கின்ற
உத்தமர்தம் உறவுவேண்டும்
உள் ஒன்று வைத்துப் புறம்பொன்று பேசுவார்
உறவு கலவாமை வேண்டும்
பெருமைபெறு நினதுபுகழ் பேசவேண் டும் பொய்மை
பேசாதிருக்கவேண்டும்
பெருநெறி பிடித்தொழுக வேண்டும் மதமான பேய்
பிடியாதிருக்கவேண்டும்
மருவுபெண் ஆசையை மறக்கவே வேண்டும் உனை
மறவாதிருக்கவேண்டும்
மதிவேண்டும்  நின் கருணை நிதி வேண்டும்  நோயற்ற
வாழ்வில் நான் வாழவேண்டும்
தருமமிகு சென்னையில் கந்தகோட் டத்துள் வளர்
தலம் ஓங்கு கந்தவேளே
தண்முகத் துய்யமணி  உண்முகச் சைவமணி
சண்முகத் தெய்வமணியே.

பாடல் 3
அன்பெனும் பிடியுள் அகப்படும் மலையே
அன்பெனும் குடில்புகும் அரசே
அன்பெனும் வலைக்குட் படுபரம் பொருளே
அன்பெனும் கரத்தமர் அமுதே
அன்பெனும் கடத்துள் அடங்கிடும் கடலே
அன்பெனும் உயிர்ஒளிர் அறிவே
அன்பெனும் அணுவுள் ளமைந்தபே ரொளியே
அன்புரு வாம்பர சிவமே.

பாடல் 4
எத்துணையும் பேதமுறாது எவ்வுயிரும்
⁠தம் உயிர்போல் எண்ணி உள்ளே
ஒத்துரிமை யுடையவராய் உவக்கின்றார்
⁠யாவர் அவர் உளந்தான் சுத்த
சித்துருவாய் எம் பெருமான் நடம்புரியும்
⁠இடம் என நான் தெரிந்தேன் அந்த
வித்தகர்தம் அடிக்கேவல் புரிந்திட என்
⁠சிந்தை மிக விழைந்த தாலோ.

snippet.title: Union Budget 2023-24: Complete Analysis - IN NEWS I Drishti IAS
snippet.description:
Finance Minister Nirmala Sitharaman in Union Budget 2023-24 has announced attractive incentives and rebates in the new income tax regime, a steep hike in capital investments, and the biggest ever outlay in railways. The Union Budget 2023-24 can be summarised in three big takeaways. In essence, Finance Minister Nirmala Sitharaman has stuck to the broader growth strategy that she unveiled in 2019-20. 
  
चर्चा के बिंदु

localized.title: Union Budget 2023-24: Complete Analysis - IN NEWS I Drishti IAS
localized.description:
Finance Minister Nirmala Sitharaman in Union Budget 2023-24 has announced attractive incentives and rebates in the new income tax regime, a steep hike in capital investments, and the biggest ever outlay in railways. The Union Budget 2023-24 can be summarised in three big takeaways. In essence, Finance Minister Nirmala Sitharaman has stuck to the broader growth strategy that she unveiled in 2019-20.

Shaakuntalam Movie also in 3D, Written & Directed by Gunasekhar, Presented by Dil Raju under Sri Venkateswara Creations in collaboration with Gunaa Teamworks, Produced by Neelima Guna.

The massively mounted film Shaakuntalam based on internationally acclaimed Kalidasa’s Sanskrit play ‘Abhijnana Shakuntalam’ is all set to release in Hindi, Telugu, Tamil, Malayalam & Kannada.  The story of Shaakuntalam revolves around the epic love story of Shakuntala and King Dushyant from Mahabharata, portrayed by Samantha and Dev Mohan.

The film is helmed by supremely proficient, Director Gunasekhar and marks a whimsical tale of love set in the Kashyapa Kanumalu (Kashmir), the grandeur and splendour of Dushyant’s Puru Dynasty making the film extremely exceptional.

snippet.description:
Vikas जी की तरह सही Skills, मेहनत, जज़्बे और जुनून के साथ करें अपना हर सपना सच: https://joshskills.app.link/YtNYUGvmVwb

https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PL1D6nWQpbEZf2bV4kpEOmee0aPcAqol19

Josh Talks brings you a series in which we will know about Dr.Vikas Divyakirti’s professional and personal lifestyle. Along with this, we will know what are his thoughts regarding UPSC Exam preparation and what his life inspirations have been.

This is Episode 02 of this series in which Dr. Vikas Divyakirti will discuss the following questions -

1. What has been the importance of Hindi and English Mediums in UPSC Results?
2. Online or Offline Education for UPSC Preparation, which is better?
3. What is Vikas Divyakirti Sir's opinion about the affordable and expensive UPSC Institutes?

Dr. Vikas Divyakirti is an IAS Trainer, Author, and Lecturer. He is the founder of Drishti IAS Coaching Classes, a UPSC Coaching Institute in Delhi. He was born in Haryana. He has done MA in Hindi literature from Delhi University. We must have heard him taking UPSC Mock Interview on Drishti IAS. From children to old people, they all are fans of his words. Many people put Dr. Vikas Divyakirti's Motivational Shorts and Videos on their Status. He also has a YouTube channel named Vikas Divyakirti. 

जोश Talks लाया है एक ऐसी सिरीज़ जिसमें हम जानेंगे Dr. Vikas Divyakirti जी की Professional और Personal Lifestyle के बारे में. साथ ही जानेंगे कि इनके UPSC Exam Preparation को लेकर क्या विचार हैं और इनकी क्या Life Inspirations रही हैं.

ये इस सिरीज़ का Episode 02 है जिसमें Dr. Vikas Divyakirti निम्नलिखित सवालों पर चर्चा करेंगे -

1. UPSC के Result में Hindi और English Medium का क्या महत्व रहा है? 
2. UPSC Preparation के लिए Online या Offline Education, क्या बेहतर है?
3. Dr. Vikas Divyakirti जी की Affordable और Expensive UPSC Institute को लेकर क्या राय है?

Dr. Vikas Divyakirti जी IAS Trainer, Author और lecturer हैं. Drishti IAS Coaching Classes जो कि Delhi में एक UPSC Coaching Institute है, ये उसके Founder हैं. इनका जन्म Haryana में हुआ. इन्होंने Delhi University से Hindi literature में MA किया है. हुमनें इनको Drishti IAS पर UPSC Mock Interview लेते हुए सुना होगा. बच्चे से लेकर बूढ़े तक इनकी बातों के Fan हैं. कईं लोग Dr. Vikas Divyakirti जी की Motivational Shorts और Videos अपने Status पर लागते हैं. इनका एक YouTube channel भी है जिसका नाम है Vikas Divyakirti. 

Dr. Vikas Divyakirti जी की ये Motivational Speech देख कर हमें Successful बनने का मार्गदर्शन और हौसला मिलेगा. 

#JoshTalksHindi #DrVikasDivyakirtiJoshTalks #DrVikasDivyakirti #vikasdivyakirtisir #vikasdivyakirti #vikasdivyakirtimotivation #vikasdivyakirtibiography #drvikasdivyakirti

Josh Talks Hindi aims to inspire and motivate you by bringing to you the best Hindi motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 7 regional languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the challenges they face in their careers or business and helping them discover their true calling in life. 

“ज़िंदगी में कुछ बड़ा करने के लिए जोश का होना बहुत ज़रूरी है.” 
इसी सोच के साथ एक शुरुआत हुई. देश के कोने-कोने से सबसे प्रेरणादायक कहानियों को चुनकर हर उस शख्स तक पहुंचाने की जो बड़े सपने देखता है. 
इसी सोच का नाम है जोश Talks. 
वो मंच जहां कई Role Models आते हैं और अपने जीवन की प्रेरणादायक कहानी हमारे साथ शेयर करते हैं. वो अपने जीवन के उन किस्सों को शेयर करते हैं जहां वो Fail हुए, उन्होंने गलतियां की, कई बार हिम्मत भी टूटी पर अपने लक्ष्य को हासिल करके ही माने. 

अगर दो शब्दों में कहा जाए, तो जोश Talks हम सबके लिए हमारे ‘बड़े भैय्या/बड़ी बहन’ की तरह है. 
जो हमेशा हमारे दोस्त बनकर हमारी बात सुनते हैं और हमें कुछ नया सिखाते हैं.
तो चलो, जोश के साथ हर Goal को हासिल करें. :)

और हां! अगर हमारे पास ऐसे लोगों की कहानियां हैं जिन्होंने अपनी मेहनत और हिम्मत के दम पर अच्छा मुकाम हासिल किया है. जिससे आज वो समाज के लिए एक Role Model बन गए हैं. 
तो, अभी लिखकर भेज देते हैं - speakers@joshtalks.com

snippet.title: जया एकादशी व्रत कथा | jaya ekadashi ki katha | ekadashi vrat katha | जया एकादशी की कहानी
snippet.description:
जया एकादशी व्रत कथा | jaya ekadashi ki katha | ekadashi vrat katha | जया एकादशी की कहानी

नमस्कार दोस्तों, आज  01 फरवरी 2023 को जया एकादशी के अवसर पर मैं आप सभी के समक्ष माघ शुक्ल पक्ष की जया एकादशी की कथा प्रस्तुत कर रही हूं। आइए शुरू करते हैं जया एकादशी की कथा पूजा विधि  महत्त्व 

धर्मराज युधिष्ठिर बोले - हे भगवन्! आप कृपा करके माघ शुक्ल एकादशी का वर्णन कीजिए। इसका क्या नाम है, इसके व्रत की क्या विधि है और इसमें कौन से देवता का पूजन किया जाता है?
श्रीकृष्ण कहने लगे कि हे राजन्! इस एकादशी का नाम 'जया एकादशी' है। इसका व्रत करने से मनुष्य भूत, पिशाच आदि योनियों से मुक्त हो जाता है, ब्रह्महत्या आदि पापों से छूट कर मोक्ष को प्राप्त होता है। इस व्रत के प्रताप से व्‍यक्ति के सभी पापों का नाश होता है और घर में सुख-संपत्ति आती है. इस व्रत को विधिपूर्वक करना चाहिए।इसका व्रत करने पर मनुष्यों को कभी प्रेतयोनि में नहीं जाना पड़ता । जो लोग एकादशी का व्रत नहीं कर पाते हैं वह भी आज के दिन विष्णु भगवान की पूजा करके जया एकादशी की कथा को सुनें,विष्णु जी के नामों को मन ही मन पाठ करें और जरुरतमंदों की सहायता करें तो इससे भी पुण्य की प्राप्ति कर सकते हैं ।
अब मैं आपको जया एकादशी के महात्म्य की एक कथा सुनाता हूँ।
Hello friends, today, on the occasion of Jaya Ekadashi on 01 February 2023, I am presenting to you all the story of Jaya Ekadashi of Magh Shukla Paksha. Let's start the story of Jaya Ekadashi, story of worship, and importance

Dharmaraja Yudhishthira said - O God! Kindly describe Magh Shukla Ekadashi. What is its name, what is the method of its fast and which deity is worshiped in it?
Shri Krishna started saying that O Rajan! The name of this Ekadashi is 'Jaya Ekadashi'. By observing this, a person is freed from the vagaries of ghosts, vampires etc., attains salvation by getting rid of sins etc. All the sins of a person are destroyed by the brilliance of this fast and there is happiness and wealth in the house. This fast should be done in a systematic way. Humans never have to go to the haunted world after fasting it. Those who are not able to observe Ekadashi fast, also listen to the story of Jaya Ekadashi by worshiping Lord Vishnu on this day, recite the names of Vishnu ji by heart and help the needy, then you can also achieve virtue by this .
Now let me tell you a story of the great significance of Jaya Ekadashi.

#jayaekadashivratkatha   #जयाएकादशी #ekadashivrat
#jayaekadashivratkatha

snippet.title: PLAYGROUND 2 AUCTION | @CarryMinati @triggeredinsaan, Scout, Ashish & Harsh Beniwal
snippet.description:
Playground is back! CarryMinati, Triggered Insaan, Ashish, ScoutOP & Harsh are trying to find the best contestants for the real money auction & pick them for their teams for the season starting 30th January streaming LIVE on YT & on Amazon miniTV! 

Voting lines for Super Subs open on Rumble, closes at 4:30 PM on 30th January. Vote here https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.robosoft.playverseStage
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*Auction rules*
• 40 contestants
• Only 28 will remain post auction
• 20 players, selected through bidding, will go directly into teams 
• 8 players will go into super subs
 • Of this, 5 players will be selected by the 5 mentors
 • And 3 players will be selected through voting on Rumble
• Player mix for teams - 1 Pro-player, 1 international player, Min. 1 player from previous season, Min. 1 female player
• Every week two players will get eliminated and new players will be selected from supers subs 
• 25L purse of each mentor to bid for players
• If a mentor has invoked an RTM card for a player during the Tryouts, they have the Right to Match the final bid on that player during the auction
• Mentors can retain players from their last season team, retained players will not be put up for auction, 35% of purse amount will be retention fee for retained player

➟ Song : Dorran 2
➟ Singer: Akay
➟ Female Lead : Kanchan Sangha

Lyrics: 

Paye ni shaapa chhalle apa change aa kalle 
Jad rabb saddu tur jana apa kite aap ni challe 
Karte sab rabb havale aape kade vair ni kadde 
Gair ton aas nayi rakhi te apne kade pair ni shadde 
Dil de doctor ne ajj tayi aashiq da ilaaj ni kareya 
Kavaa ton kathe hoke kalla ik baaj ni mareya 
Ajj tayi kade raaj nayi kita jungle vich moran ne 
Dabde nayi dabbe ton malak hath dorran ne 
Jithe kamm kare halimi nayi karna joran ne


Maade jo time ch chad gaye kise nal harkh nayi koi 
Koi sanu ki samje painda hun fark ni koi 
Koi lakh kar jaye maada mathe kade vatt ni paya 
Pandita nu future de layi main nayi kade hath dikhaya 
Sach ni koi hoya aisa jo akhan ne biyan ni kareya 
Hoya ni saadh koi aisa rabb da jine dhayan ni dhareya 
Jinna vich uddeya firda saadh pune diya loran ne 
Dabde nayi dabbe ton malak hath dorran ne 
Jithe kamm kare halimi nayi karna joran ne


Dheethan nal dheeth bade aa aunde kise guage ch haini 
Kimat meri puch ona ton jina di main range ch haini 
Chadar ton bahar kade vi nek na pair pasare 
Bolan di lod ni sanu paundi aa chupp khilare 
Sade te asar nayi kareya oh allarhan diyaan toran ne 
Vekhe kayi khunje laate jhanjar deya shoran ne 
Allarha impress karan layi na kaddiya kade tohra ne 
Dabde ni dabbe ton malak hath dorran ne 
Jithe kamm kare halimi nayi karna joran ne

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3682 - 31 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3682: Badey Guru Ji Ki Advice
--------------------------------------------------------
Taarak's boss is disappointed after the client leaves his cabin without confirming anything. He lashes out at Taarak for failing to persuade the client. Taarak is to blame for wearing a green shirt instead of a yellow one. Taarak's boss decides to fire him as a result of this. Chamapklal enters the cabin to persuade the boss, but he remains firm in his decision. Suddenly, the client returns and discusses the deal with the boss. So, how did Taarak's presentation go over with the client? So, why did the client leave the cabin quietly in the first place? Watch this episode of Laughter Riots for more.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3682, 31 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Ye kahaani hai Geet ki, jiski shaadi Dev naam ke ek NRI se hoti hai, lekin wo use pregnancy ki haalat mein akela chhodd deta hai. Aise mein Geet milti hai Maan se, jo Dev ka hi Bhai hai, lekin Donon hi apne is rishte se anjaan hain. Maan ki madad se Geet apni ek nayi zindagi shuroo karti hai aur donon mein pyaar ho jaata hai. Movie Credits

Music - Ajay - Atul

Song Credits:
Music : Ajay - Atul 
Lyrics Ajay -Atul 
Singer - Atul Gogavale
Recorded & Mixed by Vijay Dayal @ YRF studios

Music Composed, Arranged, Produced & Conducted - Ajay- Atul 
Indian percussions - Satyajit Jamsandekar, Raju Kulkarni, Jamsandekar, Dipesh Varma, Pratap Rath 
Female Chorus: Mrinmayi Dadake, Sonali Karnik, Pragati Joshi, Aditi Prabhudesai, Rucha Soman, Madhura Paranjpe

Lyrics:
भावी आमदार 

आलो म्हम्बईला जाउन मी काल 
मोठ्या साहेबांना भेटुन बी झालं 
मतदार संघामंदी लई हाल 
वाट पाहुन सफेद झाले बाल 

जिथं भरलीया सभा 
तिथं गर्दीत उभा 
असं लाख लाख भर शाऊटींगला 

किती  मागु मी टिकीट
कुनी देईना फुकट 
सोड भीत न्हाई कुनाच्या बी वॉर्नींगला  

बाल्या मोठं माझं फोटो लाव होर्डिंगला
आला भावी आमदार  न्युज मॉर्निंगला 

अंतरा १ 
साध्या वह्या वाटप करुन  केली सुरूवात 
मतदारा संग नातं माझं जोडलं 
किती किलो किलो व्हतं माझ्या अंगावर सोनं
बाल्या रोज रोज थोडं थोडं मोडलं 
करा फराळाची यादी 
आता सगळ्याच्या आधी 
करु दिवाळी पहाट साडे तीन ला 
सारा करु आटा पीटा 
मंग  उधळून नोटा 
आनु शेलिब्रेटि मोठा परफोर्मिंगला 

बाल्या मोठं माझं फोटो लाव होर्डिंगला
आला भावी आमदार  न्युज मॉर्निंगला 

अंतरा २ 

किती केली आंदोलन  , किती केले रोज ऱ्हाडे 
नाही दिला कुनी भाव कुटं नावं ना 
लावा जाहिरात माझी, आता मेन रोड वर 
सारं शुभेच्छुक त्याच्या मंदी मावना 

आता अभिनंदनाचं मला मेसेज येत्याल 
बाल्या फोन माझा  लावं चार्जिंगला 
जर मोठ्या साहेबाचा आला ताफा बिफा मोठा 
त्याला जरा तरी जागा करं पार्किंगला

बाल्या मोठं माझं फोटो लाव होर्डिंगला
आला भावी आमदार  न्युज मॉर्निंगला

snippet.title: MAAN MERI JAAN SUPREMACY I KING AFTER-PARTY INDIA TOUR AFTERMOVIE TEASER
snippet.description:
#MaanMeriJaan #ChampagneTalk #King 

In October 2022, I presented my 3rd Studio Album Champagne Talk to the World. We also set out on a Tour across 18 cities the very next day to celebrate the album with you. 

Hyderabad-Pune-Indore-Mumbai-Vadodara-Ludhiana-Nagpur-Kolkata-Delhi-Jaipur-Ahmedabad-Bengaluru-Ranchi-Delhi-Kolkata-Guwahati-Surat-Goa
And the one song that roared across the nation was Maan Meri Jaan.

It’s not possible to put into words the Magic we experienced. You all came together to make my biggest dream come true. And to prove that Kingsclan is not just a word. It’s an emotion we all feel. Together. 

Thank you for the Phenomenon. Thank you for creating the Term of the year – Maan Meri Jaan Supremacy. And thank you for being there. 

Special Thanks to Team Innovation for amazing Tour partners.

snippet.title: UP की बेटी ने India को बनाया World Champion | Crickter Archana Devi | Womens t20 World Cup
snippet.description:
#Womenst20WorldCup2023 #ArchanaDevi #up #latestnews 

नाम अर्चना देवी... काम क्रिकेट खेलना... हिमालय सा हौसला... आसमान सा इरादा... जिसने देश को वल्ड चैंपियन बना दिया... बता दें कि... भारतीय महिला अंडर-19 टीम की खिताबी जीत में अर्चना देवी की मुख्य भूमिका रही... क्रिकेटर अर्चना देवी का सफर काफी मुश्किलों से भरा रहा... सफर ऐसी की उनकी कहानी जानकर... सुनकर... देखकर सभी की आंखे नम हो जाएगी... आज हर वर्ग के लोग उनकी हिम्मत,जोश,जज्बात को देखकर तारीफ करते नहीं थक रहे हैं... आज हर किसी के जुबान पर एक ही शब्द होगा... वाह अर्चना तुने क्या कमाल कर दिया... बेटी की इस उड़ान को देखकर देश में जश्न का माहौल है... आइए जानते हैं कि... क्रिकेटर अर्चना देवी का बचपन से लेकर विश्व विजेता टीम का हिस्सा बनने तक का सफर कैसै रहा

Farq Episode 28 - [Eng Sub] - Faysal Quraishi - Sehar Khan - Adeel Chaudhry - 31st January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Farq is the story of two different individuals, Irsa (Sehar Khan) and Kamal (Faysal Quraishi) who come together to form an unusual union under compromising circumstances. 
From the outside, Irsa and Kamal seem not to be made for each other. They are too different in terms of character, life choices, desires and socio-economic background. 
On one hand, Irsa desires to live a life of luxury while Kamal is fed up with the loneliness that his house offers. Despite being together as a couple, 
will the two ever look at the truth in themselves to determine who they are and what they want in life?

snippet.title: ABDU ROZIK | BIG BOSS, STRUGGLES BEFORE FAME, GIRLFRIENDS & MORE  #ep24
snippet.description:
✯✯COMMENT BELOW about your favourite moment!✯✯

Mr. Abdu Rozik! The gentleman who has won all of our hearts! The young man who has taken the country by storm has opened up like never before. After this conversation, my soft spot for him has just gotten bigger. Not just me, but the whole team felt the same. We respect you Abdu! He generously shares intimate moments about his difficult upbringing. Which I am relieved to say are now just personal memories because he has worked extremely hard to change his fortune-less past. However, the episode also offers laughs and Abdu's views on one of Big Boss' controversies. A lot to take in but I know you'll enjoy it! ALSO, we're now stacked up with phenomenal episodes so stay tuned and subscribe to the channel!
